old_1}}% | {{corrective_action_1}} |\n| 成本偏差 | {{frequency_2}} | {{audience_2}} | {{threshold_2}}% | {{corrective_action_2}} |\n| 投资回报 | {{frequency_3}} | {{audience_3}} | {{threshold_3}}% | {{corrective_action_3}} |\n| 效率指标 | {{frequency_4}} | {{audience_4}} | {{threshold_4}} | {{corrective_action_4}} |\n\n## 8. 风险管理\n\n### 8.1 预算相关风险\n| 风险类别 | 风险描述 | 发生概率 | 影响程度 | 风险等级 | 应对策略 |\n|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n| 收入风险 | {{revenue_risk}} | {{probability_1}} | {{impact_1}} | {{level_1}} | {{strategy_1}} |\n| 成本风险 | {{cost_risk}} | {{probability_2}} | {{impact_2}} | {{level_2}} | {{strategy_2}} |\n| 执行风险 | {{execution_risk}} | {{probability_3}} | {{impact_3}} | {{level_3}} | {{strategy_3}} |\n| 外部风险 | {{external_risk}} | {{probability_4}} | {{impact_4}} | {{level_4}} | {{strategy_4}} |\n\n### 8.2 应急计划\n- **预算调整机制**: {{budget_adjustment_mechanism}}\n- **成本控制措施**: {{cost_control_measures}}\n- **资源重分配**: {{resource_reallocation}}\n- **项目优先级调整**: {{project_priority_adjustment}}\n\n## 9. 绩效指标与考核\n\n### 9.1 预算绩效指标\n| KPI | 目标值 | 权重 | 数据来源 | 考核周期 |\n|-----|--------|------|---------|---------|\n| 预算准确性 | {{budget_accuracy_target}}% | {{weight_1}} | {{source_1}} | {{period_1}} |\n| 成本控制率 | {{cost_control_target}}% | {{weight_2}} | {{source_2}} | {{period_2}} |\n| 投资回报率 | {{roi_target}}% | {{weight_3}} | {{source_3}} | {{period_3}} |\n| 资源利用率 | {{utilization_target}}% | {{weight_4}} | {{source_4}} | {{period_4}} |\n\n### 9.2 考核与激励\n- **考核对象**: {{assessment_targets}}\n- **考核周期**: {{assessment_period}}\n- **激励措施**: {{incentive_measures}}\n- **改进计划**: {{improvement_plan}}\n\n## 10. 附录\n\n### A. 预算编制依据\n- {{basis_1}}\n- {{basis_2}}\n- {{basis_3}}\n\n### B. 相关文档\n- {{related_document_1}}\n- {{related_document_2}}\n- {{related_document_3}}\n\n### C. 联系人信息\n| 角色 | 姓名 | 部门 | 联系方式 | 职责 |\n|-----|------|------|---------|------|\n| 预算负责人 | {{budget_owner}} | {{department_1}} | {{contact_1}} | {{responsibility_1}} |\n| 财务审核 | {{finance_reviewer}} | {{department_2}} | {{contact_2}} | {{responsibility_2}} |\n| 业务审批 | {{business_approver}} | {{department_3}} | {{contact_3}} | {{responsibility_3}} |\n\n---\n**预算版本**: {{budget_version_number}}\n**生效日期**: {{effective_date}}\n**审核日期**: {{review_date}}\n**批准日期**: {{approval_date}}\n**保密等级**: {{confidentiality_level}}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"cherry-deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":89,"output":3607,"cacheRead":60160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63856,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776173226963}}
